== 光環 (光象) ==
[[File:Solar_glory_at_the_steam_from_hot_spring.jpg|來自[[溫泉]]蒸氣產生的光環|thumb|right]]

{{Main|光環 (光象)}}

光環是常見涉及水滴的光學現象<ref name="1842diction">{{cite book|url=http://books.google.com/?id=5To-AAAAIAAJ&pg=PA540&lpg=PA540&dq=halo+formation+ice+atmosphere+book#v=onepage&q=halo%20formation%20ice%20atmosphere%20book&f=false|title=A dictionary of science, literature, & art: comprising the history, description, and all the terms in general use|page=540|author=William Thomas Brande and Joseph Cauvin|year=1842|accessdate=2011-04-02|publisher=Longman, Brown, Green, and Longmans}}</ref>。光環這種光學現象，看上去好像宗教上標誌著[[聖人|聖人]]的[[暈_(宗教肖像)|暈]]，是包圍著觀測測者頭部的[[後向散射|後向散射]]（綜合光的[[繞射|繞射]]、[[反射|反射]]和[[折射|折射]]）的[[光|光]]，其來源是雲中大小均勻的水滴。光環像是多種色彩同心圓的戒指，紅色在最外層，而藍色和紫色在最內圈<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.weather.gov/glossary/index.php?letter=g|title=Glossary: G|author=[[National_Weather_Service|National Weather Service]]|publisher=[[National_Oceanic_and_Atmospheric_Administration|National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration]]|date=2009-06-25|accessdate=2011-04-12|archive-date=2012-05-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120531082224/http://www.weather.gov/glossary/index.php?letter=g|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

光環的角距離與彩虹相似，範圍依據水滴的大小從5°至20°，只有觀測者在折射水滴的雲和太陽之間時才能被看見。因此，人們經常在搭乘飛機時看見光環圍繞在飛機投射在雲上的影子周圍（稱為飛機的光環）。在山上和高處的建築物也可以看見光環<ref>{{cite book|url=http://books.google.com/?id=S96s2HD0FJgC&pg=PA70&dq=angle+size+glory+book#v=onepage&q=angle%20size%20glory%20book&f=false|page=70|title=Science From Your Airplane Window|author=Elizabeth A. Wood|year=1975|publisher=Courier Dover Publications|isbn=978-0-486-23205-8}}</ref>。當有雲或霧在觀測者的下方，或地面有霧的天氣時，也會有光環。光環與[[幻日|幻日]]的光學現象有關。
